  <article>
    <pre style="white-space: normal;font-size: 1.4rem;border-bottom: thin solid #e8e8e847;padding: 0 10px 20px;margin: 0 0 20px;"><i>This is a case study for a simple, accessible User Interface for the <a href="https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/archivepix.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Astronomy Picture of the Day website</a>.
    <br><br>
    The current website is essentially unchanged from the early days of the web. As a result, it's become cumbersome to navigate<br><br>  
